        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2014-10-17 18:55:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nSince LU-4300 and LU-5556 are known not to be the cause of the LU-5077 test failures, it doesn't make sense for this patch to continue reverting them.  That increases the risk that any patches based on this one will not be able to land on master due to patch conflicts with other parts of the code.\n\nAlso, this patch itself should be rebased onto the tip of master so that the later patches are less likely to have patch conflicts.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 5
    },
