        "subject": "LU-4788 lfsck: revert LU-4300/LU-5556 and disable some tests",
        "message": "LU-4788 lfsck: revert LU-4300/LU-5556 and disable some tests\n\nRevert \"LU-4300 ldlm: ELC picks locks in a safer policy\"\nRevert \"LU-5556 target: limit bulk transfer time\"\n\nThe commit is causing out of memory failure on MDS/OSS in\ncrypto_create_tfm().\nThe LFSCK patches are blocked by these failures on Maloo.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <fan.yong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I69f7493eedfb24285e842c8367cb0238d108996d\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
